>

Kenzo entered the CR Chambor for a beast mode. It felt kinda wierd 
entering it when he wasn't damaged. After exiting he was in the body 
of a large seagull. He went to robot mode sence he couldn't walk to 
fast on the ground in that mode. While looking along at the damaged 
craft he made his way to the bridge then waited for further orders.
